<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="67" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[136,1089,189,452]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">
Recently described species is reported from 
<collectingCountry box="[773,866,189,215]" name="Austria" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">Austria</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[883,1084,189,215]" name="Czech Republic" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">Czech Republic</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[136,251,224,250]" name="Hungary" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">Hungary</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[262,369,223,249]" name="Slovakia" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">Slovakia</collectingCountry>
, 
<collectingCountry box="[381,458,223,249]" name="Serbia" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">Serbia</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry box="[517,615,223,249]" name="Albania" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">Albania</collectingCountry>
(
<bibRefCitation author="REZAC, M. &amp; PEKAR, S. &amp; JOHANNESEN, J." box="[631,832,223,251]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" pagination="263 - 287" refId="ref5575" refString="REZAC, M., PEKAR, S. &amp; JOHANNESEN, J. (2008): Taxonomic review and phylogenetic analysis of central European Eresus species (Araneae: Eresidae). - Zoologica Scripta 37: 263 - 287. https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1463 - 6409.2008.00328. x" type="journal article" year="2008">
REZÁC 
<emphasis box="[713,767,223,249]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">et al.</emphasis>
2008
</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="GRBIC, G. &amp; SAVIC, D." box="[842,1085,223,249]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" pagination="243 - 260" refId="ref4477" refString="GRBIC, G. &amp; SAVIC, D. (2010): Contribution to the knowledge of the spider fauna (Arachnida, Araneae) on the Fruska Gora Mt. - Acta entomologica serbica 15: 243 - 260." type="journal article" year="2010">GRBIC &amp; SAVIC 2010</bibRefCitation>
, 
<bibRefCitation author="NAUMOVA, M. &amp; HRISTOVSKI, S. &amp; HRISTOV, G. H." box="[136,389,257,284]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67" pagination="503 - 511" refId="ref5286" refString="NAUMOVA, M., HRISTOVSKI, S. &amp; HRISTOV, G. H. (2016): Spiders (Arachnida: Araneae) from Prespa National Park, Albania. - Acta zoologica bulgarica 68: 503 - 511." type="journal article" year="2016">
NAUMOVA 
<emphasis box="[266,321,257,283]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">et al.</emphasis>
2016
</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="4.[136,1089,189,452]" pageId="4" pageNumber="67">Our specimens correspond well to the original description, both in genital and somatic features. The females were black with yellow-orange front of the prosoma. The males had red hairs covering the posterior part of the carapace, femora of the legs II, and all segments of III and IV pairs of legs, except the tarsi, which were brownish. All males were found in spring (April–June).</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
